CREATED:20260122T150950Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us in welcoming the 2026 J. Leonard Goldner\, MD Visiting
  Professor\, Dr. Charles Saltzman\, MD\n\nWe are honored to host Charles 
 Saltzman\, MD\, the L.S. Peery\, MD Presidential Endowed Professor of Ort
 hopaedics at the University of Utah and Editor‑in‑Chief of Foot & Ankle I
 nternational and Foot & Ankle Orthopaedics.\n\nDr. Saltzman will deliver 
 his keynote lecture\,\n"Innovation & Orthopaedics: It's the Journey that.
 .."\,\noffering insights drawn from decades of leadership\, research\, an
 d mentorship in the field.\n\nDon't miss this opportunity to learn from o
 ne of orthopaedics' most influential voices.
DURATION:PT1H
