 ess practice with Mindful Movement. The 15-minute Zoom sessions will comb
 ine movement\, breathwork\, visualization and intention to create a movin
 g meditation practice that enhances relaxation and improves well-being. D
 rop in for an enhanced mindfulness experience through a focus on mobiliza
 tion.
